sequenceDiagram
    participant C as MCP Client
    participant S as MCP Server
    participant UI as User Interface
    C->>S: tools/call: search_files(query)<br/>_meta: {progressToken: "abc123"}
    Note right of S: Server begins<br/>long-running search
    S-->>C: notifications/progress<br/>token: "abc123", 20/100<br/>"Searching 200 of 1000 files"
    C->>UI: Progress bar: 20%
    S-->>C: notifications/progress<br/>token: "abc123", 60/100<br/>"Searching 600 of 1000 files"
    C->>UI: Progress bar: 60%
    S-->>C: notifications/progress<br/>token: "abc123", 100/100<br/>"Search complete"
    C->>UI: Progress bar: 100%
    S->>C: tools/call response<br/>{results: [...]}
